# SAP HANA vs Classic Databases (DB2 / Oracle)

This document explains the fundamental differences between SAP HANA
and classic relational databases traditionally used with SAP ECC,
such as DB2 or Oracle.

Understanding this shift is essential to grasp why SAP S/4HANA
requires changes in architecture, custom code, and data models.

